summary: Custom Fur Armor by me, that\'s moderately lore friendly
descriptionHtml:
[color=yellow]Check out my armor replacer! [/color] :[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3654]Killer Keo\'s Skimpy CBBE Armor Replacer[/url]

[color=yellow]Get my other custom armor here [/color] :[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28926/]Thalmor Viceroy Inquisitors Clothes[/url]

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a New Custom Armor by me using Caliente\'s Female Body or CBBE Curvy.

It\'s More Lore Friendly then my other armors

Keep in mind this is just a Female armor. 
Wearing on Male will give you a bunch of random armors.

It\'s a Full set of Light Armor including: Gloves, Boots, Hood, and Body

Can be made at the forge under Hide:
Body: 1 SabreCat Snow Pelt, 4 Leather, 6 Leather Strips
Boots: 2 Wolf Pelts, 2 Leather, 2 Leather Strips
Gloves: 1 Wolf Pelt, 2 Leather , 2 Leather Strips
Hood: 1 Fox Snow Pelt, 2 Leather, 2 Leather Strips

If there is any problems please comment them. Thanks 

As always if you like please endorse :)
author: Killer Keo
